{"tid":1201481,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪得我老母咁萌塞？","createTime":"2019-06-11T04:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T05:47:41.000Z","uid":70403,"like":61,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c27e1782fdd3d7ccf7f59f6f2819e1851a35fdb","tid":1201481,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:54:28.000Z","msg":"我同佢解釋大雄俾胖虎打嘅故事，話俾佢知要暴力反抗先有用，和平抗議點會有用。<br />\n仆佢個街竟然話暴力打人唔好，點解要暴力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問佢咁大雄點算啊？佢答<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好答我，我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌那媽，真係俾佢吹漲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n叫佢遊行，去咗就請埋你去食下午茶又唔撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇到新聞見到個差佬流哂血就話罵啲示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我又同佢講多次大雄胖虎故事，佢就話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔知，我淨係想香港和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n問佢點解中國咁好，以前啲人要偷渡嚟香港？<br />\n問佢中國咁好，點解啲高官，習總啲仔女要去外國讀書？<br />\n之後又答<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔知唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n擺明中國根本就係唔好啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">每日淨係識得食同訓，<br />\n香港發生咩事乜撚都唔知。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔撚會俾家用，直至到佢答我知。"},{"pid":"9979666c37db7cb8437b8f5b60376cb1dfaa981b","tid":1201481,"uid":70403,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"不過平時佢都算係個好媽媽嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e47c527ee76595f6d38c63ee9b19ed4b642327","tid":1201481,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:59:23.000Z","msg":"屋企唔講政治會家變<br />\n父上同我講邊有100萬出泥行　最多咪得30萬<br />\n我話翻　警方出名報細數　信就你自己諗"},{"pid":"eee28811daa7239afb49007c64b1f3e679d9b5c5","tid":1201481,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"我老豆一樣<br />\n反而我阿媽雖然唔會去遊行<br />\n但佢都認同遊行目的"},{"pid":"0cc4291c3e2181559e9da3987779efbd5bb3067e","tid":1201481,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:13:51.000Z","msg":"唔支持咪算，但都要叫佢換美金<br />\n話哂都係自己老母<br />\n同埋啲錢可以全家一齊洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebb4bfdaf38dd8424074acb023186ffb8a516de","tid":1201481,"uid":8439,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"第時踢佢入老人院 佢問點解<br />\n你答返佢:唔好問我 我唔知"},{"pid":"d47d90c00b9e29aeb467af1aaee2baeaa5dbf452","tid":1201481,"uid":101945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:17:08.000Z","msg":"食同訓 形容得好<br />\n屌 點解我屋企都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1834df7e54693acf2f53c8df2bd35cf5c8d5318a","tid":1201481,"uid":252318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:19:51.000Z","msg":"我同我老母講信我就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af51f5f03de64f9f5ea46e3fcfa21ba1c9f5eed8","tid":1201481,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:19:54.000Z","msg":"香港廢中廢老係咁,d思想價值觀錯撚哂"},{"pid":"177cd6f315212be2f2dec085403a4c41c80c1065","tid":1201481,"uid":70403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0cc4291c3e2181559e9da3987779efbd5bb3067e","tid":1201481,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:13:51.000Z","msg":"唔支持咪算，但都要叫佢換美金<br />\n話哂都係自己老母<br />\n同埋啲錢可以全家一齊洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/